skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my toolbox
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill allows you to add common household tools to your virtual toolbox. Alexa can remind you what tools you have and if you tell her, she will remember where they are. You could for example say the lawnmower is at the holiday house.
You can also create a secret code so you can discover what tools your friends have and visa versa.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
